  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determinate if the patients submitted to laparoscopic surgery
      in trendelemburg position develope more inadequate anaesthesic emergence than patients
      submitted to laparoscopic surgery in other positions.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
